abstract: Tyler Kepner On Baseball column says Texas Rangers must shake off one of the worst single-game collapses in World Series history if they wish to attain long-deferred championship.
snippet: The Texas Rangers have not had much positive history to show off in pictures in and around their locker room.
lead_paragraph: The Texas Rangers have not had much positive history to show off in pictures in and around their locker room.

headline.main: Rangers Fail to Rewrite Their History
